Program: Discovery
Title: DNA - the discovery of the 21st century?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrxbn
Last Broadcast Date: 02 February 1999
A look at the enigma of the deep-water whales, some of which have never been seen. How could one molecule include the complete code to life. A report on the findings of Francis Crick and James Watson. The programme asks, what is DNA?